Note on map data
-----------------
The MIT license above applies to the source code of this project only.
The geographic data used or generated by this project is licensed separately:

  * SRTM elevation data — Public Domain (NASA / CGIAR-CSI).
    https://srtm.csi.cgiar.org/

  * OpenStreetMap data (water, forest, etc.) — © OpenStreetMap contributors,
    licensed under the Open Database License (ODbL).
    https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright

Any redistribution of generated maps (e.g. maps/*.json) must preserve the
OpenStreetMap attribution and comply with the ODbL.
